<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Recovery Approved</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Nunito Sans", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #222;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      p {
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Account Recovery Approved</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= fullname %>,</p>
      <p>
        We are pleased to inform you that your account recovery request has been
        approved. Your account has been restored and is now active.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can log in to your account using your previous credentials. If you
        encounter any issues or have any questions, please feel free to contact
        us.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for being a valued member of our community.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The HTU LMS Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
